SIMPLE: widely
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Widely
<hw>Wide"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In a wide manner; to
a wide degree or extent; far; extensively; <as>as, the gospel was
<ex>widely</ex> disseminated by the apostles</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Very much; to a great degree or extent; <as>as, to
differ <ex>widely</ex> in opinion</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Widen</ent>⟦br⟧
